OpenCodeClaude CodeClaude DesktopCursor <p>CLI: <pre><code>opencode mcp add containerhive -- ch mcp --project ${workspace}
</code></pre></p> <p>Or JSON in <code>~/.opencode/mcp.json</code>: ~/.opencode/mcp.json<pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "containerhive": {
      "command": "ch",
      "args": [
        "mcp",
        "--project",
        "${workspace}"
      ]
    }
  }
}
</code></pre></p> <p>CLI: <pre><code>claude mcp add containerhive -- ch mcp --project ${workspace}
</code></pre></p> <p>Or JSON at user scope in <code>~/.claude.json</code>: ~/.claude.json<pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "containerhive": {
      "command": "ch",
      "args": [
        "mcp",
        "--project",
        "${workspace}"
      ]
    }
  }
}
</code></pre></p> <p>Or project-scoped in project root: .mcp.json<pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "containerhive": {
      "command": "ch",
      "args": [
        "mcp",
        "--project",
        "${workspace}"
      ]
    }
  }
}
</code></pre></p> <p>Add to <code>~/Library/Application Support/Claude/settings.json</code>:</p> ~/Library/Application Support/Claude/settings.json<pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "containerhive": {
      "command": "ch",
      "args": [
        "mcp",
        "--project",
        "/path/to/project"
      ]
    }
  }
}
</code></pre> <p>Add to <code>~/.cursor/mcp.json</code>:</p> ~/.cursor/mcp.json<pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "containerhive": {
      "command": "ch",
      "args": [
        "mcp",
        "--project",
        "${workspace}"
      ]
    }
  }
}
</code></pre>
